data.description: Very FUNCTIONAL floor plan on 1.3 acres of TRANQUILITY! You will enjoy PRIVACY & SPACE all while being in a well-established neighborhood with NO THRU TRAFFIC!  This home has a BRAND NEW ROOF (March 2023) and  NEW 2-UNIT HVAC systems! On the 1st floor you have a beautiful sitting room with lots of windows and natural light, gorgeous formal dining room, well-appointed kitchen with tons of CUSTOM CABINETS and a wraparound bar, a separate eat-in breakfast nook that connects the huge great room with gas fireplace.  Downstairs also features a laundry room with cabinetry and plumbed for an additional laundry sink which sits next to a stylish powder room is just off the foyer. Upstairs you have a huge Master Suite with gorgeous windows and a sitting area, a gigantic master bathroom with garden tub, stand up shower, and huge double vanity with built in custom cabinetry, and large walk in closet. Upstairs also features 3 additional spacious guest bedrooms and a full hall bathroom. The home also features a huge fully enclosed Florida room that is perfect for entertaining and leads to a gorgeous outdoor patio area and grilling pad that overlooks one of the biggest, fully-fenced back yards you can find in the heart of Pace with a custom built fire pit featuring a large paver deck with bistro lighting hung above for those gorgeous fall nights . The property is wooded on 3 sides giving all the serene privacy that's hard to find and much desired. The 3 CAR OVER-SIZED GARAGE is complete with a LARGE TOOL CLOSET with peg board and a nice size work area with a SERVICE DOOR leading out to the side yard.   No Active HOA, one will be listed but there is no covenant rules enforced, the HOA sends a request for $50/ yr but it is voluntary. Boats/ RV's etc. allowed.   Schedule your showing fast, this one will not sit long!!
